title: GoPro HERO11 Black
description: Capture stunning 5.3K video and photos with the GoPro HERO11 Black. Featuring HyperSmooth 4.0 video stabilization and waterproof up to 33 feet.

title: Sony WH-1000XM4 Wireless Noise-Canceling Headphones
description: Experience exceptional sound quality with industry-leading noise cancellation. The WH-1000XM4 headphones offer up to 30 hours of battery life and touch controls.

title: Nest Learning Thermostat (3rd Generation)
description: Save energy and stay comfortable with the Nest Learning Thermostat. It learns your schedule and temperature preferences to keep your home cozy.

title: Dyson Pure Cool Me Air Purifier
description: Breathe easy with the Dyson Pure Cool Me air purifier. It projects purified air where you need it most, creating a personal zone of clean air.

title: Apple iPhone 13 Pro Max
description: The iPhone 13 Pro Max introduces a pro-level camera system, a brighter Super Retina XDR display, and the power of A15 Bionic chip. Available in five stunning colors.

title: Core Water
description: Our premium reusable water bottle is made from recycled materials and features a leak-proof design. Perfect for eco-conscious individuals looking to reduce plastic waste.
